- "He didn't say nothin'."

6
00:01:05,315 --> 00:01:08,735
But yesterday
I got his answer, all right.

7
00:01:08,819 --> 00:01:10,779
My barn burned!

8
00:01:10,821 --> 00:01:14,449
<i>A barn burner is the meanest,
lowest creature there is.</i>

9
00:01:14,491 --> 00:01:17,953
I can't find against you,
Quick. There's no proof.

10
00:01:17,995 --> 00:01:20,330
